@node HISTORY "History"

@{b}History@{ub}
@{b}=======@{ub}

11.7.98 - v1.0
  - initial release.

14.7.98 - v1.1
  - DEVICE and UNIT tooltypes are now interpreted.

17.7.98 - v1.2
  - fixed colors on standard palette settings (ie. on white menu background and white important text).

4.8.98 - v1.3
  - fixed time display
  - added AUTOPLAY, AUTOEJECT, FONTNAME, FONTSIZE, XPOS, YPOS and HEIGHTADD tooltypes

@endnode

